name: D3velopers
overview:
Aim to provide offshore cost-effective web development & design services.

The company is on the outlook of affiliation and partnerships with companies who provide web development/design services to partner with us so that they can work either on some of their projects collaboratively or exclusively.

The focus of the company is to raise the standards of offshore organizations by providing companies/startups with the best code quality for their applications. They strongly believe that for any organization or e-business to proceed, its important that the architecture of the application is really scalable and tailored in such a manner that it can cater millions of users without any hassles. Also the code-base has to follow the best programming practices and it has to be laid down in such an easier manner that the new developer to join the project doesn’t have to go through a lot of problems understanding it completely.
